PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-1084 of May 25, 1993 by deleting from the Schedule thereto the words "Maureen Silcoff Toronto, Ontario"; and appointment of MAUREEN SILCOFF of Toronto, Ontario, as part-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending May 31, 1998, effective November 1, 1996.
